text:
@lukeoneil47 A Garibaldi/Garibaldi spritz is an underrated brunch cocktail.

(For those reading: it’s a Campari&amp;OJ. Pull back on the Campari so it’s not too “woof.” For the spritz, add prosecco or sparkling water, depending on how forward you want it.

Mocktail: replace Campari w/ pom juice!)
